dct_title_s: Hunterdon and Somerset counties, New Jersey 1914
dct_description_sm: Farm Journal map of Hunterdon and Somerset counties, New Jersey. The roads in each township are numbered to correspond with the Farm Journal Farm Directory of the county. Railroads and inter-urban electric lines are indicated.
